riod change rate will merge in the future.\nHowever, our results rather point to the presence of tertiary companions in the\nobserved systems and/or spot activity on the surface of the binary components.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Jun 2017 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Aug 2017 07:31:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-24"}
